name: Evol Era's
description:
"Evol Era's" was my entry into the #evolartcomp ran by KidEight. The concept is a Gevol family photo which has been split between 3 notable era's over the last 100 years. In each era i've tried to capture the vibe of the times with colors, styles and background architecture. For the keen eyed people, I've also put in a number of references to the Gevols brand and the creator, KidEight. 

Evol Era's is minted as a 1/1 piece of work 

4000 x 4000 Pixel Canvas
